senselogic.sitevision.api.render.velocity

Interface VelocityAccess.ArticleUtilConstants

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ArticleUtil
    Enclosing interface:
    VelocityAccess

    public static interface VelocityAccess.ArticleUtilConstants
    Get methods for accessing field constants defined in ArticleUtil.

    The sole purpose of this interface is to provide access to ArticleUtil constants in Velocity, e.g: $articleUtil.PROPERTY_LAST_MODIFIED_DATE

    Since:
    Sitevision 3.6.2
    Author:
    Magnus LÃ¶vgren
